text: There are several lakes named Mud Lake within the U.S. state of Ohio. * Mud Lake, Ashland County, Ohio. * Mud Lake, Stark County, Ohio. * Mud Lake, Summit County, Ohio. * Mud Lake, Summit County, Ohio. * Mud Lake, Williams County, Ohio. ==References== * USGS-U.S. Board on Geographic Names Category:Lakes of Ohio
title: Mud Lake (Ohio)
